        <th>Arguments</th>
        <th>What it means</tr>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>prompt</td>
        <td>
            The text displayed in the input box.
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Title</td>
        <td>
            The text displayed in the input box’s title bar (optional).
        </td>
